Access:
cd "/home/m-taha/OS Project"

Commands:
Monitor Bash File: chmod +x monitor.sh
Modules Bash File: chmod +x modules/*.sh
GUI Bash File: chmod +x monitor_gui.sh
Combined Bash File Execution: chmod +x "/home/m-taha/OS Project/monitor.sh" && chmod +x "/home/m-taha/OS Project/modules/"*.sh
GUI Bash File (for all scripts): chmod +x monitor.sh monitor_gui.sh modules/*.sh

Executable File:
./monitor.sh
./monitor_gui.sh

Apts Installed:
Overall: sudo apt update
For CLI: sudo apt install procps psmisc tree
For GUI: sudo apt install zenity -y

For Running On Preference:
CLI: ./monitor.sh
GUI: ./monitor.sh --gui
